313
00:14:26,399 --> 00:14:27,899
All right, there you go.

314
00:14:27,900 --> 00:14:30,970
One Whammy Special,
with Whammy Slaw.

315
00:14:30,971 --> 00:14:33,873
There's a used Band-Aid
in my coleslaw.

316
00:14:33,874 --> 00:14:35,607
My gosh, let me take care of that.

317
00:14:35,609 --> 00:14:37,243
Get out of here before

318
00:14:37,244 --> 00:14:39,477
