you Commie bastard!

319
00:14:39,479 --> 00:14:41,658
If you're from the census,
you take me off your list!

320
00:14:43,349 --> 00:14:45,618
You never did have much
of a bedside manner, Champ.

321
00:14:45,619 --> 00:14:47,986
