325
00:14:54,126 --> 00:14:55,360
Oh, this feels like home.

326
00:14:56,128 --> 00:14:57,462
Are you all right?

327
00:14:57,463 --> 00:14:59,631
Yeah, I'm fine.
Better now.

328
00:14:59,633 --> 00:15:02,133
Okay, let's break
the huddle here, huh?

329
00:15:03,235 --> 00:15:04,602
Okay. All right.
All right.

330
00:15:04,604 --> 00:15:06,471
You get back here! Oh!

331
00:15:06,472 --> 00:15:08,474
