332
00:15:08,475 --> 00:15:10,942
CHAMP: So, anyway,
Harken sat me down, he said,

333
00:15:10,943 --> 00:15:14,113
"Champ, you're a dangerous
alcoholic, a racist,

334
00:15:14,114 --> 00:15:16,481
