339
00:15:26,025 --> 00:15:28,293
Fortunately,
on the way out the door,

340
00:15:28,294 --> 00:15:30,328
I fake a work injury.

341
00:15:30,330 --> 00:15:32,398
With the settlement,
I bought this place.

342
00:15:32,399 --> 00:15:34,578
Well, I'm glad to see you
landed on your feet, Champ.

343
00:15:35,366 --> 00:15:37,235
Listen, can I ask you a question?

344
00:15:37,236 --> 00:15:38,503
