349
00:15:46,446 --> 00:15:48,313
Yeah. We use mainly bats.

350
00:15:48,315 --> 00:15:49,648
What?

351
00:15:49,649 --> 00:15:52,283
Yeah. But the good quality kind.

352
00:15:52,284 --> 00:15:55,220
That's the most horrible
thing I've ever heard.

353
00:15:55,221 --> 00:15:57,255
Yeah? You got to do
what you got to do, right?

354
00:15:57,256 --> 00:15:59,457
So what you got to do
is serve fried bats?

355
00:15:59,459 --> 00:16:02,160
Yep. Do you know
what they call bats?

356
00:16:02,162 --> 00:16:04,562
Bats.
"Chicken of the cave."

357
00:16:04,563 --> 00:16:06,498
No one calls them
"chicken of the cave."

358
00:16:06,499 --> 00:16:08,366
