aren't you?

385
00:17:03,123 --> 00:17:04,323
(BRIAN GROWLS)
(CAMERA CLICKING)

386
00:17:04,324 --> 00:17:07,492
Yeah. Oh, I like
what's happening!

387
00:17:07,493 --> 00:17:10,395
Oh, that's it.
Yeah. Yeah.

388
00:17:10,396 --> 00:17:13,131
Oh, you little fuzzball,
that's... Oh!

389
00:17:15,334 --> 00:17:17,502
I got it.
(ALL APPLAUDING)

390
00:17:17,503 --> 00:17:19,670
It's not getting
any better than that.

391
00:17:20,506 --> 00:17:22,508
That's brilliant!
Yeah, yeah.

392
00:17:22,509 --> 00:17:24,608
Hey, Brian, you have any
time for the little people?

393
00:17:27,746 --> 00:17:29,814
Well, I'll be a son of a bitch.

394
00:17:30,481 --> 00:17:32,150
(ALL LAUGHING)

395
00:17:33,451 --> 00:17:35,653
Hey, Brian.
Champ! How you doing?

396
00:17:35,654 --> 00:17:37,256
Hey!

397
00:17:37,257 --> 00:17:38,557
Wow. This is a...
