400
00:17:42,061 --> 00:17:45,197
Welcome.
Welcome to my doj'.

401
00:17:45,198 --> 00:17:46,432
This place is spectacular!
It's amazing.

402
00:17:46,432 --> 00:17:48,133
A bit chaotic today.

403
00:17:48,134 --> 00:17:50,134
We got the <i>Cat Fancy</i>
<i>cover coming out.</i>

404
00:17:50,135 --> 00:17:51,737
You know how that can be. Ooh.

405
00:17:51,738 --> 00:17:53,305
I've been living in a tent
for the last two years.

406
00:17:53,306 --> 00:17:54,640
Oh, yeah, this is not that.

407
00:17:54,641 --> 00:17:56,407
We got a sauna in the kitchen.

408
00:17:56,409 --> 00:17:58,176
A lot of people think that's weird,

409
00:17:58,177 --> 00:18:00,078
but I keep wine in it.

410
00:18:00,079 --> 00:18:02,314
I'm not a wine guy, but I
know you got to keep it hot.

411
00:18:02,315 --> 00:18:04,383
Oh, and check this out.

412
00:18:04,384 --> 00:18:06,518
This...
This was fun.

413
00:18:06,519 --> 00:18:07,819
We shot this over
two weeks in Prague.

414
00:18:07,820 --> 00:18:09,488
RON: Wow.

415
00:18:09,489 --> 00:18:11,722
You know what they call cats?

416
00:18:11,723 --> 00:18:14,259
Chicken of the rail yard.
No.

417
00:18:14,259 --> 00:18:16,228
