Don't indulge him.

418
00:18:16,229 --> 00:18:17,695
Yeah.
CHAMP: There's a lot of meat.

419
00:18:17,696 --> 00:18:19,530
But I love it. (CHUCKLES)

420
00:18:19,531 --> 00:18:22,166
And what's so great about
