ALL: Yes!

490
00:20:57,589 --> 00:20:58,856
(LAUGHING JOYFULLY)
ED: Of course.

491
00:20:58,857 --> 00:21:00,558
Of course you are.

492
00:21:00,559 --> 00:21:02,426
Oh, for heaven's sake.

493
00:21:02,428 --> 00:21:04,663
