scenario by which peace
could be reached with Israel?

1811
01:18:31,807 --> 01:18:33,742
ARAFAT: Peace is what burns in my heart.
I am committed to...

1812
01:18:33,743 --> 01:18:34,722
What was... Excuse me.

1813
01:18:35,277 --> 01:18:37,244
What happened to the...

1814
