1848
01:20:00,194 --> 01:20:01,261
Yes!

1849
01:20:01,829 --> 01:20:02,997
Great!

1850
01:20:02,998 --> 01:20:04,832
All right!

1851
01:20:04,833 --> 01:20:06,801
I don't believe it!
You did it, Ron!

1852
01:20:06,802 --> 01:20:08,601
Oh, my goodness.
Thanks, Freddie.

1853
01:20:09,970 --> 01:20:11,939
I don't deserve this.

1854
01:20:11,940 --> 01:20:13,539
It was a team effort.
It really was.

1855
01:20:22,917 --> 01:20:24,586
KENCH: <i>Now,</i>
<i>ladies and gentlemen,</i>

1856
01:20:24,587 --> 01:20:26,921
<i>we all know there's one reason</i>

1857
01:20:26,922 --> 01:20:30,324
<i>that GNN has gotten to the top.</i>

1858
01:20:30,326 --> 01:20:33,261
<i>And that reason is the greatest
bloody newsman in the world.</i>

1859
01:20:33,261 --> 01:20:35,296
<i>Long may he reign!</i>

1860
01:20:35,297 --> 01:20:36,997
<i>Mr. Ron Burgundy!</i>
<i>(CROWD CHEERING)</i>

1861
01:20:36,998 --> 01:20:38,097
Yeah, Ron! Yeah!

