01:21:13,068 --> 01:21:14,636
Let's blaze.

1867
01:21:14,636 --> 01:21:17,104
Yeah. To hell
with Ron Burgundy.

1868
01:21:18,372 --> 01:21:20,239
We did it, my onyx hellion.

1869
01:21:22,644 --> 01:21:23,644
You're magic!

