No other way
to put this, but...

1893
01:22:51,065 --> 01:22:52,266
You're blind.

1894
01:22:52,268 --> 01:22:55,136
Milton, I'm an anchorman.

1895
01:22:55,136 --> 01:22:58,605
I read the news off the teleprompter.
It's what I do!

1896
01:22:58,606 --> 01:23:00,240
How will I live?

1897
01:23:00,242 --> 01:23:01,643
I'm no career counselor,

1898
01:23:01,644 --> 01:23:03,345
but there are
many things you can do.

1899
01:23:03,345 --> 01:23:05,579
Be an oracle, or a mystic.

1900
01:23:05,581 --> 01:23:07,481
Clearly, there must be something

1901
01:23:07,483 --> 01:23:10,985
in this new-fangled office
of yours that can help me!

1902
01:23:10,987 --> 01:23:12,386
Settle down.
There's got to be
something in here!

1903
01:23:12,387 --> 01:23:14,122
Settle down!
(SHOUTING)

1904
01:23:14,122 --> 01:23:15,990
Zombies! Zombies!

1905
01:23:15,992 --> 01:23:17,256
Ahh!

1906
01:23:18,560 --> 01:23:20,860
If you get my hands
on me, I'll kill you.

1907
01:23:22,329 --> 01:23:24,032
NARRATOR:
<i>The world of the blind.</i>

1908
01:23:24,033 --> 01:23:25,667
<i>Ron Burgundy, a man who had</i>

1909
01:23:25,667 --> 01:23:28,302
<i>flourished in a visual medium,</i>

1910
01:23:28,304 --> 01:23:31,538
<i>had forever entered</i>
<i>this realm of darkness.</i>

1911
01:23:31,539 --> 01:23:34,507
<i>♪ Always lonely</i>

1912
01:23:35,143 --> 01:23:37,677
<i>♪ Always looking</i>

1913
01:23:39,346 --> 01:23:43,516
<i>♪ To get even with the men</i>
