1914
01:23:46,186 --> 01:23:48,288
<i>♪ That was Billy</i>

1915
01:23:48,289 --> 01:23:49,791
(BARKING)
(KNOCKING ON DOOR)

1916
01:23:49,792 --> 01:23:50,791
Who is it?

1917
01:23:53,560 --> 01:23:55,764
Ron, it's us!

1918
01:23:55,765 --> 01:23:57,332
RON: I'm sure you gentlemen

1919
01:23:57,332 --> 01:23:59,533
