1920
01:23:59,534 --> 01:24:03,238
I hope you like Triscuits
and some pimento loaf.

1921
01:24:03,238 --> 01:24:05,204
Still hot off the griddle!

1922
01:24:05,506 --> 01:24:07,442
There we go.

1923
01:24:07,443 --> 01:24:09,622
Well, everyone at the station
really misses you, Ron.

1924
