Don't eat that.

1933
01:24:28,695 --> 01:24:30,364
What about Linda?
She hasn't called.

1934
01:24:30,365 --> 01:24:31,332
Linda's pretty busy.

1935
01:24:31,332 --> 01:24:34,802
Ron, I'm going
to need your recipe.

1936
01:24:34,804 --> 01:24:36,570
So, Ron, what do you do
with yourself all day?

1937
01:24:36,572 --> 01:24:38,405
