and I think I'm dead.

1941
01:24:44,680 --> 01:24:46,113
Every day?

1942
01:24:46,114 --> 01:24:48,216
Yes! Every day!

1943
01:24:48,216 --> 01:24:51,185
And then I begin what's called
The Great Adventure.

1944
01:24:51,186 --> 01:24:53,454
Making breakfast.

1945
01:24:53,456 --> 01:24:56,091
I've eaten everything
from nails to drink coasters.

1946
01:24:56,091 --> 01:24:58,626
One time I bit hard
into a marble ashtray,

1947
01:24:58,627 --> 01:25:00,761
