Completely shattered my teeth.

1949
01:25:05,434 --> 01:25:07,668
Couldn't you tell the ashtray
wasn't hot like a waffle?

1950
01:25:07,670 --> 01:25:10,471
No! I couldn't!
Because I'm blind!

1951
01:25:10,472 --> 01:25:14,175
